      "content": "it just feels so heavy. what you're saying about \"stopping the performance\" sounds peaceful, but it still feels like so much effort just to exist. if the person inside is truly gone, then this body is just a burden that won't stop demanding things. it feels like there's no real way to truly close the chapter while this thing is still walking around.",
